      "section_index": 0,
      "section_kind": "weather_opening",
      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 10.0,
      "text": "It is currently cloudy in Berlin-Tempelhof with a temperature of 37 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 18.034,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 14.747,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a0097ad8556"
      ],
      "end": 23.512,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2"
      ],
      "start": 18.034,
      "text": "The focus for frontier AI is shifting from simple responses toward complex, real-time interaction."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a0097ad8556"
      ],
      "end": 35.929,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 23.512,
      "text": "NVIDIA is pushing this evolution with a new AI-Q Blueprint on Oracle Cloud Infrastructure. The tool helps developers move beyond single-question bots to build production-grade agents capable of multi-turn conversations."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a0097ad8556",
        "a98b363e62e",
        "adef89dd539"
      ],
      "end": 58.935,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 35.929,
      "text": "While NVIDIA scales the cloud, other players are optimizing how these models behave on local hardware and through human interfaces. Google is using a method called frozen Multi-Token Prediction to increase the speed and efficiency of Gemini Nano models on Pixel devices. At the same time, MiniMax has released Speech 2.8 to make synthetic AI voices sound more natural and lifelike."
    },
    {
      "end": 61.492,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 58.935,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 68.43,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 61.492,
      "text": "This afternoon will be cloudy with rain chances up to 43 percent and temperatures between 34 and 41 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 71.352,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 68.43,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 77.195,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 71.352,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 86.69,
      "id": "p9",
      "index": 9,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 77.195,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
